tly proposed by Sabzikar\nand Meerschaert leads to physically very different behaviour with a seemingly\nparadoxical ballistic long time scaling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 16:52:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
