ications for the nature\nof galaxies most likely to have O32 values associated with significant LyC\nescape. Finally we consider the optimal strategy for JWST spectroscopic\ninvestigations of galaxies at $z\\gtrsim10$ where the strongest rest-frame\noptical lines are no longer visible with NIRSpec.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 18:09:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2019 21:29:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-21"}
