l modes available to a 21\ncm measurement. However, we also show that this effect can be largely\neliminated by a modified redundant-baseline calibration strategy that relies\npredominantly on short baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Sep 2018 21:15:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 May 2019 21:59:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-31"}
