 medium may be an important AGN\nfeedback process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Sep 2018 02:05:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Oct 2018 03:19:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
